column1: Description
Internet goes down for 20 minutes.
Alien Invasion.
Global Recession.
YOLO!
You are a woman.
Buy your friend a game console.
You are stupid.
You dump your partner. They get drunk.
You remember you have student loans.
Some sports game is happening in your city. Apparently it's a big deal.
Apparently global warming is real.
Your shitty business idea fails predictably.
You drop your smartphone.
Twitter is down. You try to tweet about it.
Drake's new album drops.
Make fun of North Korea online. Get nuked.
Your dealer discovers socialism on Wikipedia. Weed prices decrease.
You win a fight over which came first, the chicken or the egg.
Buy your friend an elephant.
Drunk tweet about failed Kickstarter campaign.
Become morbidly obese.
Be THAT guy.
Drunk dial your ex.
Cut someone off in traffic because you're an asshole no matter how often you quote Gandhi.
Give someone a boomerang. They throw it away. It comes back.
You quote Marilyn Monroe on your Facebook page.
Your Facebook has been hacked. Friends hate you.
Emotionally blackmail friend to go to the bar with you.
You correct someone's grammar on the Internet.
You win a cruise. You send your annoying friend.
Listen to a cool NPR podcast while driving. Cause a 42 car pileup.
Spend rent money on tequila shots for your friends.
Buy a Prius. Tell everyone about your Prius.
Accidentally join ISIS.
Sell your friend's Twitter account.
Your condom broke.
Apple announces new laptop. You buy it.
You finish last. Get a participation trophy.
Start a business selling useless hipster shit.
Starbucks increases prices by $0.1.
You finish a TV series. Your life still sucks.
Spring break! Accidentally sleep with your cousin.
You just bought an iPhone. Apple releases a new model. You can't afford it.
You get drunk and eat cake. You tweet about it.
You can't afford your water bill, so you stop showering.
Get annoyed by friend singing viral song. Punch him.
Join a pyramid scheme. Convince your friends to join.
Become a freelancer. You do not have any skills.
You get divorced.
Do ecstasy at a party. It wasn't ecstacy.
Go on Facebook and see your friends doing cool stuff. Your life is an embarassment.
You walk into a bar. It hurts.
You try to buy a house. You don't have any money.
Visit a print shop. They're out of paper.
Evade Taxes. Get caught because you tweeted about it.
Make fun of North Korea online. Get made fun of back.
You look at yourself in the mirror.
Your life sucks.
Your friend doesn't file taxes. You tell the IRS for a reward. There is no reward.
You become Vegan. Tell a friend.
Become a hipster.
Your partner dumps you. You get drunk.
You dump your partner. You get drunk.
Have a pool party. You don't have a pool.
Get a face tattoo in Vegas.
Someone else looks at your face.
Taxes on alcohol are abolished for 24 hours. Everything goes to shit.
Fly to Vegas.
Visit Thailand and post lots of pictures nobody gives a shit about.
Nuclear Holocaust.
Start breeding kittens for fun and profit.
Your Macbook dies. You steal a charger from a friend.
Start a revolution to abolish the government. It fails.
Gift someone tickets to a meditation retreat.
Go to Coachella. Spend all your rent money listening to Maroon 5. You are a moron.
Your boss actually notices you exist.
Have an existential crisis.
Attack people on the internet about social issues you don't know much about.
Buy accordion. Realize you are an idiot. Sell accordion.
Get married.
You go to Hawaii to find yourself. You do a lot of weed and stop showering.
Get herpes in Vegas.
Use student loans to go Whiskey tasting.
You remember Firefly is still cancelled.
You don't know what to do with your life.
Your dealer finishes an MBA at a local college. Weed prices increase.
Run with scissors.
You get hit by a car and die.
You start learning Yoga. Doesn't help anything.
You can't even.
You convince someone to go to Burning Man. You both get herpes.
You discover you are a lesbian and break up with your partner.
You are ugly.
Sell a smart car to friend, program it to come back to you every night.
Volunteer for Hunger Games. Win.
Boss asked to fill in your timesheets for past month.
You get caught growing weed in your attic.
You throw a birthday party.
You finally watch The Wire.
You're jet lagged after traveling. You don't shut up about it.
You lose your Facebook password.
Go to college since you're useless at everything.
Buy a smart car.
Refuse to obey a cop.
Make fun of North Korea online. Get poisoned.
You spend hours getting your moustache perfect. Realize you are worthless.
There's an elephant in the room. It ignores you.
You visit a friend. You steal their beer, and then leave.
Your tax got returned. Twice. Go to jail.
Get a corporate job. Blog about it.
Point laser pointer at army helicopter. It's not appreciated.
You opened Vegan restaraunt, but quickly run out of Vegans as demand is high.
President of your country accidentally likes your photo. All your friends leave you.
Your friends are having shots. You are not invited.
You insult cop checking your documents and live stream it.
You visit Brazil. Get mugged.
You just bought an iPhone. Apple releases a new model. You buy it.
Your self-driving car gets pulled over for going too slow. Google tweets at you.
Think before you do, be unpopular amongst friends.
Drunk call yourself.
Accidentally deleted your screenplay.
Accidentally consume non cruelty-free product.
You are a white male. Take a card from someone else.
Tried to fly while being brown.
Go to a conference. You adult, you.
Get into political argument on Facebook.
You find out the Maldives will be gone soon. Visit them.
Buy suspenders. Sell them because you look like an idiot.
You go to a PETA demonstration in leather jacket. It hurt, but you're trending on Worldstar.
Watch documentary about social issues. Do nothing.
Petition government to increase number of hours in a day to 25.
Start a Kickstarter. Flip a coin to determine whether it succeeds or fails.
Wear Nirvana Tshirt. Walk somewhere.
You discover that a horse is cheaper than an iPhone. You buy a horse.
You still haven't finished your Liberal Arts degree after six years.
This card does nothing, but takes a while.
The rent for your apartment was raised. You cannot afford it and live in a box.
There is no hope.
You sell your Facebook profile to Russian hackers, including your friends.
You encounter a series of unfortunate events.
Meditate for 3 hours, still feel anxious.
You illegally download 3 seasons of Lost, binge-watch it.
You are black.
Get hit by a smart car. Nothing happens.
You go surfing. On the internet.
You drink shitty wine by yourself at 2 am on a Wednesday. You are a disgrace.
You help cops find a lost pig, making you a national hero.
Drunk call your mom.
Quit your job because you hate the system, bro.
Grow a beard. This improves your self worth for some reason.
Get a good job. Just kidding.
Go to a rave. Get stepped on.
You take responsibility at work.
Buy a unicycle. Sell it. Buy a bicycle like a normal fucking person.
You got a viral song stuck in your head, get punched by all friends but feel happy about it.
Today is earth day, you celebrate offline and alone.
Remind all of your friends in Facebook to support your Indiegogo campaign.
Get a life. For 2 days.
You visit Brazil for carnival. You can't find it.
You go on a much needed vacation, despite being unemployed.
Get an escort in Vegas.
You have a good day. Everybody hates you.
Have a party at your shitty apartment.
Give up smoking for 3 weeks. Be very proud of yourself.
Eat instant ramen all week.
There's an elephant in the room. You ignore it.
You find a cool new coffee place. It closes down.
You thought you didn't need health insurance.
You complete your PhD in African Philosophy. Strangely, employers don't seem to care.
Get a job at a hip new startup. They don't make any money.
Sell energy bracelets to your idiot friends.
You can't decide whether to go for a broccoli or kale smoothie.
Pretend to appreciate Whiskey because you have low self-esteem.
You think the world is flat. You tweet insulting messages to scientists who are sheep.
Learn an awesome yo-yo trick. You are still unemployed.
Donate your kidney to a friend.
Go to Movie Premier. Watch international movie nobody gives a shit about.
Loudly promote charitable cause on social media. Don't actually donate yourself.
Claim you like PBR. You do not like PBR.
Become a guru.
Your internet provider went broke. You actually go outside.
Oprah accidentally tweets your Twitter name.
Uber is on strike, go play bowling.
Pretend to not like popular music.
You find money on the road and tell nobody. Dick.
You realise you're 30 and living with your mother.
You hurt yourself longboarding. Pretend it happened surfing.
You lie about your height in your Tinder profile.
Your mom adds you to her Netflix account.
Drunk call your boss.
Go to the gym once. Post inspirational photo.
Vote for a Conservative political candidate.
You are not caught growing weed in your attic.
Become enlightened.
New taxes. You rant about it on social media.
Join Greenpeace to save dinosaurs, be considered stupid by your friends.
Win the Lottery. Lose most of it to a ponzi scheme on the way home.
You play Cards Against Humanity alone because you have no friends.
You see Kim Jong-Un at Disney Land.
We discover the Higgs Boson. You pretend to understand what this means.
You did the laundry by yourself. Tweet about it.
You pay off your student loans. Now you just have a useless degree.
You open a bar without being a total hipster idiot. It does moderately well.
You stop eating like a fat pig for one day.
You start growing flowers. Tell everyone about this.
You find an ancient treasure. You give some away to make people like you.
You are a plastic surgeon. Everyone hates you.
Delete your facebook profile. Don't brag about it.
Convince somebody that going to Siberia is good idea.
You accidentally post a YouTube video of you crying and eating cake. It goes viral.
You are Asian.
Convince your friend to watch Game of Thrones.
Delete your facebook profile. Brag about it.
You are fired from McDonalds.
You have no friends.
New Game of Thrones episode is out today.
You bring a member of the opposite sex home. They leave immediately.
You start a book club with your friends. Everyone pretends to read.
You manage to avoid death and taxes.
Your lesbian life partner asks to spend time together.
Due to a computer glitch, everyone wins the lottery.
You are actually somewhat useful to society.
The pub nearby has free beer. You stand in queue for 4 hours on a Wednesday.
Get married in Vegas because you saw it on Friends.
Vote for Socialist political candidate.
After a wild party, wake up with your friend's significant other.
Someone publically insults you. You angrily blog about it later.
Strong alcohol tax is increased by 1%.
Accidentally post sexy photo of your ex on Instagram. They get famous.
You are perfectly average and in all ways largely unimpressive.
You finally start getting invited to parties. As designated driver.
Win a company retreat challenge. Your price is a can of sardines.
